<h2>The legal bit</h2>
<p><b>•</b> The promotional discount is only available to individual Bupa customers.  </p>
<p><b>•</b> During the pandemic and lockdown, some gyms may be closed. These are clearly highlighted on the Hussle’s website and will be re-activated as soon as they are available again.</p>
<p><b>•</b> This offer is a one-time usage only and users can only take out one membership. </p>
<p><b>•</b> This offer is valid for 33% off the purchase of a Monthly+ pass, for as long as you’re a Bupa customer and as long as Hussle are still active on the Everyday Rewards by Bupa.  </p>
<p><b>•</b> The user is committed to a 3-month minimum membership to gain the discount, after which they can cancel or pause their membership at any time</p>
<p><b>•</b> The voucher code will not be accepted by participating gyms directly, can only be redeemed against the purchase of a Hussle pass on the Hussle website and has no equivalent cash value.</p>
<p><b>•</b> The list of available gyms is provided on the <a href="https://www.hussle.com/" target="_blank">Hussle’s website</a> and may change from time to time.  </p>
<p><b>•</b> Some locations are excluded from this promotion. If you want to check exclusions with Hussle, either chat to them 9am-9pm daily using the LiveChat icon on the <a href="https://www.hussle.com/" target="_blank">Hussle website</a>Hussle website, or drop them an email at info@hussle.com</p>
<p><b>•</b> Please remember to take photographic ID with you when you visit the gym to gain access.  </p>
<p><b>•</b> The voucher code can be redeemed up until 23.59hrs 31st December 2021.      </p>
<p><b>•</b> Once added to a Hussle account, the voucher will be valid to purchase a pass for 30 days.  </p>
<p><b>•</b> Credit card details will be required at checkout and at the end of the discounted period the Monthly+ Pass will auto-renew at the advertised rate; however, you can cancel the pass at any time and will not be charged.</p>
<p><b>•</b> If the voucher expires before a user uses it, the voucher will not be reapplied.</p>
<p><b>•</b> For full Terms &amp; Conditions of use please refer to the <a href="https://www.hussle.com/legal/terms/" target="_blank">Hussle’s website</a>.      </p>
<p><b>•</b> Hussle reserves the right to hold, void, cancel, suspend, or amend the offer where it becomes necessary to do so. By accepting this offer, you are deemed to have accepted and agreed to be bound by these terms and conditions. This promotion will be governed by English law and subject to the jurisdiction of the English courts.</p>
